<promed@promedmail.org>

[This is the official confirmation of the outbreak reported earlier. In has no reference to the owner's shenanigans butchering and selling the meat of the dead cow. But it confirms that there was only a single beast involved. To see a map of the Ukraine showing Zaporizhia region and Melitopol on the SE and bordering on the Sea of Azov go to http://www.lib.utexas.edu/maps/europe/ukraine_adm93.jpg. - Mod.MHJ

A HealthMap/ProMED-mail map can be accessed at: http://healthmap.org/r/1z-2.]
